::Shadow Wing::

She handed the scanner to him. "Are you sure about this? I mean, I am 
willing to do this." She looked at the she scanner.  She was just so 
sure he would have jumped at the chance to have a wolf as a partner. 
And have her as the wolf partner.  "Well, if your sure about it, them 
I won't try to change."  She looked at the floor.
